<plot>In the vein of a medieval tradition of Antwerp the so called "Pilgrimstable" is held every year during the Holy Week. Twelve affluent citizens provide twelve needy elderly men with a copious dinner. This ritual is inspired and reminiscent of the Last Supper.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?131799</url></doc>
